<?php

Class Product

{

    private $priceTaxExcl;
    private $quantity ;
    private int $idLang;
    private $LanguageName;
    /**

        return $this;

        return $this;

    }

        return $this;

    public function getQuantity()
    {
        return $this->quantity;
    }

    /**
     * Set the value of quantity
     */
    public function setQuantity($quantity): self
    {
        $this->quantity = $quantity;

        return $this;
    }

    }

        return $this;
    }

/**
